    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that it got messy, but wasn't the immediate goal just to prevent a massacre in benghazi? if they hadn't stepped in, wouldn't it have been a huge humanitarian disaster? surely that's some kind of success in itself, even if the aftermath was bad.",
