      "content": "that seems a bit harsh though. you're saying it was a failure because it didn't build a perfect new state, but is it fair to judge a humanitarian rescue mission by the standards of long-term regime change? shouldn't we be able to separate the success of saving lives from the political fallout that happened years later?",
